---
title: HelloHero: Double Herbed Beef & Roast Veggie Toss with Yoghurt & Chargrilled Capsicum Relish
description: Feel the sweet sense of bliss when you sit down to eat this bowl of nutritious deliciousness. The fresh veggies, roasted to
warm perfection create a bed for the tender beef strips to rest on. A delicious capsicum relish and yoghurt combo will have you feeling like you’re on a sunny holiday.

